                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Au fond d'un sérail inutile",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Que fait parmi ses icoglans",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Le vieux successeur imbécile",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Des Bajazets et des Orcans ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Que devient cette Grèce altière,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Autrefois savante et guerrière,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et si languissante aujourd'hui ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Rampante aux genoux d'un Tartare,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Plus amollie, et plus barbare,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Et plus méprisable que lui ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Au fond d'un sérail inutile\nQue fait parmi ses icoglans\nLe vieux successeur imbécile\nDes Bajazets et des Orcans ?\nQue devient cette Grèce altière,\nAutrefois savante et guerrière,\nEt si languissante aujourd'hui ;\nRampante aux genoux d'un Tartare,\nPlus amollie, et plus barbare,\nEt plus méprisable que lui ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Tels n'étaient point ces Héraclides,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Suivants de Minerve et de Mars,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Des Persans vainqueurs intrépides,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Et favoris de tous les arts ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Eux qui, dans la paix, dans la guerre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Furent l'exemple de la terre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Et les émules de leurs dieux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Lorsque Jupiter et Neptune",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Leur asservirent la fortune,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Et combattirent avec eux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tels n'étaient point ces Héraclides,\nSuivants de Minerve et de Mars,\nDes Persans vainqueurs intrépides,\nEt favoris de tous les arts ;\nEux qui, dans la paix, dans la guerre,\nFurent l'exemple de la terre\nEt les émules de leurs dieux,\nLorsque Jupiter et Neptune\nLeur asservirent la fortune,\nEt combattirent avec eux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Mais quand sous les deux Théodoses",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Tous ces héros dégénérés",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Ne virent plus d'apothéoses",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Que de vils pédants tonsurés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Un délire théologique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Arma leur esprit frénétique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "D'anathèmes et d'arguments ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Et la postérité d'Achille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Sous la règle de saint Basile,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Fut l'esclave des Ottomans.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais quand sous les deux Théodoses\nTous ces héros dégénérés\nNe virent plus d'apothéoses\nQue de vils pédants tonsurés,\nUn délire théologique\nArma leur esprit frénétique\nD'anathèmes et d'arguments ;\nEt la postérité d'Achille,\nSous la règle de saint Basile,\nFut l'esclave des Ottomans."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Voici le vrai temps des croisades.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Français, Bretons, Italiens,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "C'est trop supporter les bravades",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Des cruels vainqueurs des chrétiens.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Un ridicule fanatisme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Fit succomber votre héroïsme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Sous ces tyrans victorieux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Écoutez Pallas qui vous crie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "« Vengez-moi ! vengez ma patrie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Vous irez après aux saints lieux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Voici le vrai temps des croisades.\nFrançais, Bretons, Italiens,\nC'est trop supporter les bravades\nDes cruels vainqueurs des chrétiens.\nUn ridicule fanatisme\nFit succomber votre héroïsme\nSous ces tyrans victorieux.\nÉcoutez Pallas qui vous crie\n« Vengez-moi ! vengez ma patrie !\nVous irez après aux saints lieux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "« Je veux ressusciter Athènes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Qu'Homère chante vos combats,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Que la voix de cent Démosthènes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Ranime vos cœurs et vos bras.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Sortez, renaissez, Arts aimables,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "De ces ruines déplorables",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Qui vous cachaient sous leurs débris ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Reprenez votre éclat antique,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Tandis que l'opéra-comique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Fait les triomphes de Paris.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Je veux ressusciter Athènes.\nQu'Homère chante vos combats,\nQue la voix de cent Démosthènes\nRanime vos cœurs et vos bras.\nSortez, renaissez, Arts aimables,\nDe ces ruines déplorables\nQui vous cachaient sous leurs débris ;\nReprenez votre éclat antique,\nTandis que l'opéra-comique\nFait les triomphes de Paris."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "« Que des badauds la populace",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "S'étouffe à des processions,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Que des imposteurs à besace",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Président aux convulsions,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Je rirai de cette manie ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Mais je veux que dans Olympie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Phidias, Pigalle, ou Vulcain,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Fassent admirer à la terre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Les noirs sourcils du dieu mon père,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Et mettent la foudre en sa main.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Que des badauds la populace\nS'étouffe à des processions,\nQue des imposteurs à besace\nPrésident aux convulsions,\nJe rirai de cette manie ;\nMais je veux que dans Olympie\nPhidias, Pigalle, ou Vulcain,\nFassent admirer à la terre\nLes noirs sourcils du dieu mon père,\nEt mettent la foudre en sa main."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "« C'est par moi que l'on peut connaître",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Le monde antique et le nouveau ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Je suis la fille du grand Être,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Et je naquis de son cerveau.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "C'est moi qui conduis Catherine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Quand cette étonnante héroïne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Foulant à ses pieds le turban,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Réunit Thémis et Bellone,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Et rit avec moi, sur son trône,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "De la Bible, et de l'Alcoran.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« C'est par moi que l'on peut connaître\nLe monde antique et le nouveau ;\nJe suis la fille du grand Être,\nEt je naquis de son cerveau.\nC'est moi qui conduis Catherine\nQuand cette étonnante héroïne,\nFoulant à ses pieds le turban,\nRéunit Thémis et Bellone,\nEt rit avec moi, sur son trône,\nDe la Bible, et de l'Alcoran."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "« Je dictai l'Encyclopédie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Cet ouvrage qui n'est pas court,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "A d'Alembert, que j'étudie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "A mon Diderot, à Jaucourt ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "J'ordonne encore au vieux Voltaire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "De percer de sa main légère",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Les serpents du sacré vallon ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Et, puisqu'il m'aime et qu'il me venge,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Il peut écraser dans la fange",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Le lourd Nonotte et l'abbé Guion. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Je dictai l'Encyclopédie,\nCet ouvrage qui n'est pas court,\nA d'Alembert, que j'étudie,\nA mon Diderot, à Jaucourt ;\nJ'ordonne encore au vieux Voltaire\nDe percer de sa main légère\nLes serpents du sacré vallon ;\nEt, puisqu'il m'aime et qu'il me venge,\nIl peut écraser dans la fange\nLe lourd Nonotte et l'abbé Guion. »"
        }
    ],
